modName: Barmaid Minidress SevenBase More Bounce TBBP Standalone - DELETED
descriptionHtml:
Description:
Barmaid Minidress conversion for the SevenBase MORE BOUNCE TBBP.

Weight support, for fast testing open the console and enter "help pcweight" then left click on your character and tape "setNPCweight 0" or 100 if you are already using the min weight.


Instalation:
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.


Requirement:
Only download unpack and enjoy.


How to get it:
Very Simple... You can craft the minidress at any forge with a single leather strip, or simply use the console and enter "help barmaid" then "player.additem ******** 1" , where ***** is the code that you must use to get the item.


Special Thanks:
tiwa44 for this beautifull outfit.
